BFN 

  [Text] Shanghai, May 28 (XINHUA) -- Visiting Russian Prime 
Minister V. S. Chernomyrdin this afternoon toured the Pudong new 
area and two bridges in Shanghai, China's largest industrial 
center. 
  The Russian prime minister also paid his respects at the 
monument to Pushkin. 
  Chernomyrdin and his party, accompanied by He Guangyuan, 
chairman of the Chinese Government Reception Committee and 
minister of the machine-building industry, flew in here this 
morning from Beijing. 
  This evening Mayor Huang Ju of Shanghai met Chernomyrdin and 
his party. 

